Turn around and walk to the black coffee table.
Put the credit card down on the coffee table to the right of the keys.
Walk over to the small black table to the left of the chair.
Pick up the credit card that;s behind the lamp.
Walk back over to the black coffee table.
place the credit card on the coffee table to the left of the first credit card.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the middle of the tv stand, and turn right to face the tv.
Pick up the red credit card on the tv stand.
Turn right, take a few steps, and then turn right towards the black coffee table.
Place the credit card on the coffee table.
Turn left and walk towards the small circle table with the lamp.
Pick up the red credit card behind the lamp on the table.
Turn around and head back towards the coffee table.
Place the credit card to the left of the other card on the table.

pick up the credit card on top of the black cabinet in front of the television
turn around, then make a right around the center coffee table and face it
place the card in front of the television remote on the black table
turn around, then make a right to face the black side table with the lamp
pick up the credit card behind the lamp on the black side table
return to the black center coffee table and face the same side you did before
